description: Imperalis Holding Corp. does not have significant operations. Previously, the company, through its subsidiary, CannaCure Sciences, Inc., engaged in the development, marketing, and sale of cannabidiol (CBD)-based personal care and cosmetic products. The company was formerly known as Coloured (US) Inc. and changed its name to Imperalis Holding Corp. in March 2011. The company was incorporated in 2005 and is headquartered in Las Vegas, Nevada. Imperalis Holding Corp. is a subsidiary of BitNile, Inc.
